					Let $A$ be the event that $N=2$.\\
					Let $B$ be the event that ${S_1=2,S_2=0}$.\\
					$P(A)=\frac{25}{100}==\frac{1}{4}$\\
					$P(B)=\frac{4}{100}==\frac{1}{25}$\\
					$P(B \cap A)=\frac{1}{100}$\\
					$P(B|A)=\frac{P(A \cap B)}{P(A)}=\frac{1}{100}\frac{4}{1}=\frac{1}{25}=P(B)$\\
					$\therefore$ independence

